io.mosip.registration.device.scanner.wia

Enum WiaImagePropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WiaImagePropertyType>
      • io.mosip.registration.device.scanner.wia.WiaImagePropertyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com4j.ComEnum, Serializable, Comparable<WiaImagePropertyType>

    public enum WiaImagePropertyType
extends Enum<WiaImagePropertyType>
implements com4j.ComEnum

    The WiaImagePropertyType enumeration specifies the type of the value of an image property. Image properties can be found in the Properties collection of an ImageFile object.
